OL,3,CTemperatures set to reach over 30
OL,4,Cdegrees in Jersey
OL,6,FTemperatures in Jersey are expected to
OL,7,Fexceed 30 degrees over the weekend (10-
OL,8,F11th August).
OL,10,FThe hot weather has been welcome news
OL,11,Ffor organisers of the Battle of
OL,12,FFlowers and Guernsey's South Show.
OL,14,FHowever, Jersey's government has
OL,15,Fissued guidance reminding islanders
OL,16,Fthat extreme heat can cause
OL,17,F"exhaustion, heatstroke, and
OL,18,Fdehydration".
