OL,6,FThey are asking islanders to "avoid
OL,7,Fgoing outside during the hottest time
OL,8,Fof day", "drink plenty of water" and
OL,9,F"leave strenuous activities for later
OL,10,Fon in the day when it is cooler".
OL,12,FThe government added: "Older people
OL,13,Fand children are particularly at risk".
